metadata.description: ShroomDK is a collection of NFTs that unlock the ability to query the most comprehensive blockchain data in Web3, including data from Solana, Ethereum, Flow, Near, Thorchain, Avalanche, Algorand, Polygon, and many more. The ShroomDK NFT works as your API key for access to exclusive data applications, benefits, and insights. Your SDK NFT can also be upgraded via Spores, which will unlock further power-ups and product features. Holding an SDK NFT will also give you exclusive access to gated channels in the Flipside Crypto Discord, a vibrant community of data analysts and crypto-minded NFT collectors. Each day a random number of new mints drop. When mints run out for the day grab an invite code from a fren or check OpenSea.
